### checksum handling for cmdi resources
A straightforward problem set is the file integrity check for collections of metadata and primary data. Metadata and primary
language research data hosted at the IDS are very heterogenous by nature. What is important in terms of file integrity 
is to divide them into two groups
1. Resources that are based on projects finished where changes are mainly corrections to the data provided.
2. Resources that are based on projects running with frequent changes to files, additions of related data, or other 